</li></ul><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-105_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-b42e6cb9-b3ae-4844-a81b-1c20fd81d6ab"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content "><em><strong>Outcome</strong> - Learners engage more deeply, retain more, and are better prepared to apply knowledge in practice.</em>
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-108_">4. Link learning to real-world outcomes</h3><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-110_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-03e5a91e-0ae5-415d-9f45-9ad97edf819a"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Staff are more likely to care about training if they understand its practical impact. Make that connection clear:
