</span></p><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-331_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-5dac82e3-8653-4ed2-b9fd-dffe2d5c2930"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">These digital touchpoints foster accountability and reinforce progress.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-140_">6. Involve line managers and internal trainers</h3><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-142_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-0ab7cf4f-ec84-459f-a803-44c1900163d5"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Sustainable engagement isn’t just the job of L&amp;D. When managers take an active role in learning, outcomes improve.
