</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-145_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-146_">Real-time dashboards to track team training
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-148_">Supervision prompts and discussion starters
</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-150_">Templates for recognising learner achievement. 
