</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-155_">7. Recognise, reward, and reflect
</h3><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-157_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-afddec7f-978e-4f17-8564-ddc8c451e032"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Even in mandatory training, recognition matters. Foster a culture where learning achievements are celebrated.
<br></span></p><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-288_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-65525952-bcc5-43d1-82d4-4bad7cfd91aa"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Ways to recognise progress:
</span></p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-160_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-161_">Issue digital badges or CPD certificates
